    • Method Detail

      • createCache

        public static <I> DFACacheOracle<I> createCache​(net.automatalib.alphabet.Alphabet<I> alphabet,
                                                MembershipOracle<I,​Boolean> mqOracle)
        Creates a cache oracle for a DFA learning setup.

        Note that this method does not specify the implementation to use for the cache. Currently, a DAG (createDAGCache(net.automatalib.alphabet.Alphabet<I>, de.learnlib.oracle.MembershipOracle<I, java.lang.Boolean>)) is used; however, this may change in the future.

        Type Parameters:
        I - input symbol type
        Parameters:
        alphabet - the input alphabet
        mqOracle - the membership oracle
        Returns:
        a Mealy learning cache with a default implementation
